@end ifnotinfo

@item Implicit function.

@c ===beg===
@c plot2d (x^2-y^3+3*y=2, [x,-2.5,2.5], [y,-2.5,2.5])$
@c ===end===
@example
(%i1) plot2d (x^2-y^3+3*y=2, [x,-2.5,2.5], [y,-2.5,2.5])$
@end example

@ifnotinfo
@image{figures/plotting3,8cm}
@end ifnotinfo

@item Parametric function.

