@end defvr

@c -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
@anchor{x}
@defvr {Plot option} x [x, @var{min}, @var{max}]

When used as the first option in a @mref{plot2d} command (or any of the
first two in @mref{plot3d}), it indicates that the first independent variable
