@end defvr

@c -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
@anchor{ztics}
@defvr {Plot option} ztics [ztics, @var{z1}, @var{z2}, @var{z3}], @
[ztics, @code{false}], ztics, noztics

Defines the values at which a mark and a number will be placed in the z
